@startuml
title Figure 5.8: View Dashboard Sequence Diagram

actor Administrator
participant "Login Page\n(public/login.html)" as Login
participant "Dashboard Script\n(public/js/script.js)" as Script
participant "API Server\n(src/server.js)" as Api
participant "Orders Store\n(src/orders.js)" as Orders
participant "Bot Status\n(getSystemStatus)" as Status

Administrator -> Login : Enter username and password
Login -> Script : attemptLogin()
Script -> Api : POST /api/login
Api --> Script : auth token
Script --> Administrator : Redirect to dashboard
Script -> Api : GET /api/orders
Api -> Orders : getAllOrders()
Orders --> Api : order list
Api --> Script : JSON orders
Script -> Api : GET /api/status
Api -> Status : getSystemStatus()
Status --> Api : ready/qr/state
Api --> Script : status JSON
Script --> Administrator : Render table, charts, and connection panel

@enduml
